<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<manifest xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android" android:versionCode="11" android:versionName="1.1.7" package="jp.ksksue.app.terminal">
	<uses-sdk android:minSdkVersion="13" />
	<uses-feature android:name="android.hardware.usb.host" />
	<application android:label="Android USB Serial Monitor Lite" android:icon="res/drawable-ldpi/terminal.png" android:debuggable="true">
		<activity android:label="Android USB Serial Monitor Lite" android:name=".AndroidUSBSerialMonitorLite" android:launchMode="singleTask" android:configChanges="0x80">
			<intent-filter>
				<action android:name="android.intent.action.MAIN" />
				<category android:name="android.intent.category.LAUNCHER" />
			</intent-filter>
			<intent-filter>
				<action android:name="android.hardware.usb.action.USB_DEVICE_ATTACHED" />
			</intent-filter>
			<meta-data android:name="android.hardware.usb.action.USB_DEVICE_ATTACHED" android:resource="res/xml/device_filter.xml" />
		</activity>
		<activity android:name=".AndroidUSBSerialMonitorLitePrefActivity" />
		<activity android:name=".WordListActivity" />
	</application>
</manifest>
